A Simple Ruby Wrapper around the Bizo API (http://developer.bizo.com/)

Example Usage:

require 'rubygems'
require 'bizo'

client = Bizo::Client.new "YOUR_API_KEY", "YOUR_API_SECRET_KEY"
bizographics = client.classify :title => "accountant", :email => "accountingdude@somecompany.com"

client.taxonomy 

... etc

